    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Chertovica 是一款以近战为主的黑暗幻想射击游戏。</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莉莉丝亲自将你从永恒的沉睡中唤醒。恶魔降临到你的世界，而你就是要阻止他们的人。你是选择光明，成为一名圣骑士，还是选择黑暗，获得吸血鬼领主的力量？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/b5a250ba62c4b2b1fabb306d34ba0482.poster.avif?t=1748761332\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/b5a250ba62c4b2b1fabb306d34ba0482.webm?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/b5a250ba62c4b2b1fabb306d34ba0482.mp4?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >拔出你的剑，装上你的手枪，在被附身的前人类、Divožienky、狂狼和其他试图将这个世界变成地狱的害虫中杀出一条血路。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/64c2618154592a787e47aa923c3606ac.poster.avif?t=1748761332\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/64c2618154592a787e47aa923c3606ac.webm?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/64c2618154592a787e47aa923c3606ac.mp4?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索隐藏在半坍塌墙壁背后的秘密。探索绝望的黑暗地下墓穴或本应是你最后安息之地的古老修道院。体验恶魔入侵的浓厚氛围，但究竟是恐怖来自地狱，还是你这个恐怖来到了地狱？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/7f74b5de622c013f1af57ba7847632ee.poster.avif?t=1748761332\" width=800 height=224 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/7f74b5de622c013f1af57ba7847632ee.webm?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3320270/extras/7f74b5de622c013f1af57ba7847632ee.mp4?t=1748761332\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
